---
---
<section class="das-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> · <a href="/#solutions">Solutions</a> · DBS</div>
    <div class="das-hero-content">
      <div class="das-hero-meta-row">
        <div class="das-monogram">DBS</div>
        <div class="das-hero-tag">Solution · Code DBS</div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="h-display das-hero-title">Dosang Business Suite.</h1>
      <p class="lead das-hero-lead">
        도상 통합 비즈니스 운영 솔루션. SAP 표준 위에 도상의 컨설팅 경험을 모듈화한 운영 패키지.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="das-meta">
      <div class="das-meta-item"><div class="k">Status</div><div class="v">In Development</div></div>
      <div class="das-meta-item"><div class="k">Platform</div><div class="v">SAP S/4HANA</div></div>
      <div class="das-meta-item"><div class="k">Deployment</div><div class="v">Private / RISE</div></div>
      <div class="das-meta-item"><div class="k">Time-to-value</div><div class="v">TBD</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title-row">
      <div><div class="eyebrow">01 / Overview</div></div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="h-2 das-title">개발 진행 중.</h2>
        <p class="lead measure">DBS는 현재 개발 단계로, 상세 사양은 추후 공개 예정입니다. 사전 관심 등록은 Briefing 요청을 통해 가능합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section das-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow das-cta-eyebrow">Next</div>
        <h2 class="h-1 das-cta-title">DBS Early Access 등록</h2>
        <p class="das-cta-lead">개발 진행 상황과 Early Access 신청은 별도 안내드립니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn--primary">Request Briefing <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .das-hero { background: #0f2440; color: #fff; padding: 160px 0 96px; }
  .das-hero .breadcrumb { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .das-hero .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
  .das-hero-content { margin-top: 32px; max-width: 880px; }
  .das-hero-meta-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .das-monogram { width: 56px; height: 56px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .das-hero-tag { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .das-hero-title { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .das-hero-lead { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .das-meta { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 32px; margin-top: 56px; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
  .das-meta-item .k { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .das-meta-item .v { font-size: 14px; color: #fff; }
  .section-title-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 32px; align-items: start; }
  .das-title { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .das-cta { background: #0c1926; color: #fff; }
  .cta-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 48px; align-items: center; }
  .das-cta-eyebrow { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .das-cta-title { color: #fff; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .das-cta-lead { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 560px; margin: 0; font-size: 17px; }
  @media (max-width: 1023px) { .section-title-row, .cta-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .das-meta { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .das-meta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
